      "text": "Consider admission for:\nBilirubin > 20\nPT 50% above normal, INR >2\nHypoglycemia\nHypoalbuminemia\nAny\nGI bleeding\nUncontrolled nausea/vomiting, pain\nSignificant comorbidity, immunocompromised, elderly",
